g a troubling trend of similar legal actions focused on child safety.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/location-exposed-age-checks-failed-snap-sued-over-minors-rape-after-she-connected-with-assaulter-on-snapchat/articleshow/131982447.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/location-exposed-age-checks-failed-snap-sued-over-minors-rape-after-she-connected-with-assaulter-on-snapchat/articleshow/131982447.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T10:10:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131982469,imgsize-220790.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Venezuela, Japan and California shaken by powerful quakes within hours]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131980797.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A day of powerful seismic activity saw major earthquakes strike Venezuela, Japan, and California. Venezuela experienced the most devastating impact with twin quakes causing fatalities and building collapses. Japan's northeast coast was hit by a strong tremor, while northern California also registered a significant quake. Experts confirm these events are unrelated, occurring on separate fault lines.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-venezuela-japan-and-california-shaken-by-powerful-quakes-within-hours/articleshow/131980797.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/watch-venezuela-japan-and-california-shaken-by-powerful-quakes-within-hours/articleshow/131980797.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T08:43:29+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131980919,imgsize-135949.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Lunatic': Donald Trump enters shouting match with fellow Republican over Iran]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131980909.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lunatic-donald-trump-enters-shouting-match-with-fellow-republican-over-iran/articleshow/131980909.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/lunatic-donald-trump-enters-shouting-match-with-fellow-republican-over-iran/articleshow/131980909.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T08:34:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131981039,imgsize-69698.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["It's a piece of s**t": Streamer Clavicular sparks backlash after brutal France rant goes viral]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131979670.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Streamer Clavicular has sparked controversy after criticizing France during a livestream following his visit. He complained about poor Wi-Fi, infrastructure, roads, cleanliness, and his overall experience, saying he had hoped to enjoy the country but left disappointed. The viral clip divided social media, with some viewers agreeing that he was sharing his personal experience, while others criticized him for making sweeping remarks about France and its people.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/its-a-piece-of-st-streamer-clavicular-sparks-backlash-after-brutal-france-rant-goes-viral/articleshow/131979670.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/its-a-piece-of-st-streamer-clavicular-sparks-backlash-after-brutal-france-rant-goes-viral/articleshow/131979670.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131979670,imgsize-105641.cms"/></item></channel></rss>